hing.'=>'Every artist here was already vouched in by the community — if that trust is enough for you, turn this on to embed any link an artist submits, immediately, with no allowlist check and no AI review at all (the settings below are skipped entirely while this is on). Off by default. Only enable this if you are comfortable that a bad actor who made it through admission could embed a link to anything.','Every recipient\'s copy is translated individually into their own language, so a very long message is costly to translate for the whole community. Please shorten it and send it again.'=>'Every recipient\'s copy is translated individually into their own language, so a very long message is costly to translate for the whole community. Please shorten it and send it again.','Excerpt word limit'=>'Excerpt word limit','Failed'=>'Failed','Failed recipients'=>'Failed recipients','Failed recipients reset to pending — they will be retried on the next few cron cycles.'=>'Failed recipients reset to pending — they will be retried on the next few cron cycles.','Failed to fetch actor document.'=>'Failed to fetch actor document.','Failed to insert attachment.'=>'Failed to insert attachment.','Feature artwork in the shared gallery (subject: exact title)'=>'Feature artwork in the shared gallery (subject: exact title)','Feature this artwork in the gallery overview'=>'Feature this artwork in the gallery overview','Featured'=>'Featured','Featured artworks are always chosen first when selecting one work per artist for the homepage overview.'=>'Featured artworks are always chosen first when selecting one work per artist for the homepage overview.','Federated posts under this medium will carry a content warning on the Fediverse (e.g. Mastodon) unless the artist turns it off for a specific piece.'=>'Federated posts under this medium will carry a content warning on the Fediverse (e.g. Mastodon) unless the artist turns it off for a specific piece.','Fee'=>'Fee','Fetches unseen messages immed