ly to artwork, biography, and event drafts. Default: 7.','How long we retain your data'=>'How long we retain your data','How many artists must co-sign a proposal to change the community size cap before it opens as a full community vote.'=>'How many artists must co-sign a proposal to change the community size cap before it opens as a full community vote.','How many artwork cards the gallery overview shows per page. Pool is built proportionally across all artists; featured artworks are preferred. Default: 12.'=>'How many artwork cards the gallery overview shows per page. Pool is built proportionally across all artists; featured artworks are preferred. Default: 12.','How many tags the AI should generate per artwork. Referenced as {tag_count} in the system prompt.'=>'How many tags the AI should generate per artwork. Referenced as {tag_count} in the system prompt.','How this node introduces itself to the network.'=>'How this node introduces itself to the network.','How to share your work — send an email to:'=>'How to share your work — send an email to:','HTTP %d'=>'HTTP %d','HTTP Signature verification failed.'=>'HTTP Signature verification failed.','https://agnosis.art'=>'https://agnosis.art','Icon'=>'Icon','Icon color'=>'Icon color','Icon settings'=>'Icon settings','Icon size'=>'Icon size','Icon vertical align'=>'Icon vertical align','Icon-only link to the artist’s biography.'=>'Icon-only link to the artist’s biography.','Icon-only link to the artist’s events archive.'=>'Icon-only link to the artist’s events archive.','Icon-only links have no text baseline of their own — use this if they sit too high or low next to the artist name once Icon size is changed from the default.'=>'Icon-only links have no text baseline of their own — use this if they sit too high or low next to the artist name once Icon size is changed from the default.','Idle'=>'Idle','If the link was correct, its destination may simply not be from a source this site automatically embeds.'=>'If the link was correct, its destination may simply not be from a source this site automatically embeds.','If you did not make this request, you can ignore this email — your account remains unchanged.'=>'If you did not make this request, you can ignore this email — your account remains unchanged.','If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — nothing will be removed unless you click one of the buttons above.'=>'If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — nothing will be removed unless you click one of the buttons above.','If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — your %s will remain published.'=>'If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — your %s will remain published.','If you didn\'t apply, simply ignore this email — nothing happens until this link is clicked.'=>'If you didn\'t apply, simply ignore this email — nothing happens until this link is clicked.','If you didn\'t request this, please contact the site admin right away.'=>'If you didn\'t request this, please contact the site admin right away.','If you didn\'t request this, simply ignore this email — you will not be subscribed.'=>'If you didn\'t request this, simply ignore this email — you will not be subscribed.','If you have questions, please contact the site admin.'=>'If you have questions, please contact the site admin.','If you made this request, click the link below to confirm. This action is permanent and cannot be undone.'=>'If you made this request, click the link below to confirm. This action is permanent and cannot be undone.','If you want to permanently remove this %s, click the button below. This action cannot be undone.'=>'If you want to permanently remove this %s, click the button below. This action cannot be undone.','If your photo was taken on an iPhone, try switching Settings → Camera → Formats to "Most Compatible" before taking or sending it, or use "Options" in Mail to send it as a JPEG.'=>'If your photo was taken on an iP