 confirmation link — nothing is deleted until you click it.','Send batch size'=>'Send batch size','Send Invitation'=>'Send Invitation','Send message'=>'Send message','Send new artwork to be published.'=>'Send new artwork to be published.','Send Now'=>'Send Now','Send Test'=>'Send Test','Sender email address'=>'Sender email address','Sender name'=>'Sender name','Sending…'=>'Sending…','Sends a minimal ping ("Reply with the word: ping") using the configured API key.'=>'Sends a minimal ping ("Reply with the word: ping") using the configured API key.','Sends a minimal ping using the configured API key.'=>'Sends a minimal ping using the configured API key.','Sends one plain-text email from the same community identity used for review/vote/vouch mail. Reaching your inbox is a good sign; landing in spam or not arriving at all confirms a real deliverability problem regardless of what the checks above say.'=>'Sends one plain-text email from the same community identity used for review/vote/vouch mail. Reaching your inbox is a good sign; landing in spam or not arriving at all confirms a real deliverability problem regardless of what the checks above say.','Sensitive by default'=>'Sensitive by default','Sensitive content'=>'Sensitive content','Sent'=>'Sent','Sent at'=>'Sent at','Sent to artist'=>'Sent to artist','Sent to the AI as the system instruction. Use {tag_count} and {excerpt_words} as tokens — they are replaced with the values below.'=>'Sent to the AI as the system instruction. Use {tag_count} and {excerpt_words} as tokens — they are replaced with the values below.','Settings'=>'Settings','Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid perspective distortion.'=>'Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid perspective distortion.','Short bio'=>'Short bio','Short description'=>'Short description','Shown in the header of outgoing HTML emails (submission review, removal confirmation, rejection notice, invitations, and both newsletters) in place of the plain "✦ Site Name" text. Leave empty to keep the text wordmark. Displayed at up to 40px tall — any width or aspect ratio works.'=>'Shown in the header of outgoing HTML emails (submission review, removal confirmation, rejection notice, invitations, and both newsletters) in place of the plain "✦ Site Name" text. Leave empty to keep the text wordmark. Displayed at up to 40px tall — any width or aspect ratio works.','Shown near the top of the "Send Invitation" email below (an "Apply to join" link and site name follow automatically — no need to add either here). Two or three short paragraphs is plenty. Standing copy, not cleared after use like the newsletter intros above — translated automatically when an invitation is sent in a language other than the site\'s own.'=>'Shown near the top of the "Send Invitation" email below (an "Apply to join" link and site name follow automatically — no need to add either here). Two or three short paragraphs is plenty. Standing copy, not cleared after use like the newsletter intros above — translated automatically when an invitation is sent in a language other than the site\'s own.','Side length of the square agnosis-thumb size used in submission cards and dashboard. Default: 512. Existing images need to be regenerated after changing this value.'=>'Side length of the square agnosis-thumb size used in submission cards and dashboard. Default: 512. Existing images need to be regenerated after changing this value.','Signature header is missing required fields (keyId, headers, signature).'=>'Signature header is missing required fields (keyId, headers, signature).','Signature header is required.'=>'Signature header is required.','Signature keyId does not belong to the activity actor.'=>'Signature keyId does not belong to the activity actor.','Signature must cover the Date header.'=>'Signature must cover the Date header.','Signature on a POST request must cover the Digest header.'=>'Signature on a POST request must cover t