n sent.'=>'Thanks — your message has been sent.','Thanks — your message has been sent. You can reach out to this artist again a little later.'=>'Thanks — your message has been sent. You can reach out to this artist again a little later.','Thanks, %s!'=>'Thanks, %s!','That date could not be understood.'=>'That date could not be understood.','That does not look like a valid link (must start with http:// or https://).'=>'That does not look like a valid link (must start with http:// or https://).','That does not look like a valid timezone (e.g. "Europe/Madrid").'=>'That does not look like a valid timezone (e.g. "Europe/Madrid").','That doesn\'t look like a valid web address.'=>'That doesn\'t look like a valid web address.','That is already the current cap.'=>'That is already the current cap.','The %1$s at %2$s is due to send in about a day. Agnosis drafted an intro from what\'s new since the last issue:'=>'The %1$s at %2$s is due to send in about a day. Agnosis drafted an intro from what\'s new since the last issue:','The %1$s community has opened a vote to change the membership size cap to %2$s. The vote closes on %3$s.'=>'The %1$s community has opened a vote to change the membership size cap to %2$s. The vote closes on %3$s.','The %1$s community has opened a vote to remove a member. The vote closes on %2$s.'=>'The %1$s community has opened a vote to remove a member. The vote closes on %2$s.','The %s community has admitted you as an artist. Welcome!'=>'The %s community has admitted you as an artist. Welcome!','The application by %s has closed without reaching the admission threshold. No action required.'=>'The application by %s has closed without reaching the admission threshold. No action required.','The artist sent no subject line or message with this submission — let the image speak entirely for itself.'=>'The artist sent no subject line or message with this submission — let the image speak entirely for itself.','The artist\'s account and all published work have been permanently deleted from %s.'=>'The artist\'s account and all published work have been permanently deleted from %s.','The artwork has been published to the gallery.'=>'The artwork has been published to the gallery.','The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight on, with the camera parallel to the canvas.'=>'The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight on, with the camera parallel to the canvas.','The artwork itself has not been altered — only the photograph quality was corrected.'=>'The artwork itself has not been altered — only the photograph quality was corrected.','The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in front of the artwork, parallel to its surface.'=>'The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in front of the artwork, parallel to its surface.','The cap must be zero or a positive number.'=>'The cap must be zero or a positive number.','The community has %d days to vote. We will let you know the outcome by email.'=>'The community has %d days to vote. We will let you know the outcome by email.','The community removal vote has closed with a majority in favor.'=>'The community removal vote has closed with a majority in favor.','The community removal vote has closed. The required majority was not reached and the artist\'s membership remains active.'=>'The community removal vote has closed. The required majority was not reached and the artist\'s membership remains active.','The community voted to change the membership size cap to %1$s (proposal #%2$d). The new cap is now in effect.'=>'The community voted to change the membership size cap to %1$s (proposal #%2$d). The new cap is now in effect.','The contact form on your page is now turned off.'=>'The contact form on your page is now turned off.','The event has been published.'=>'The event has been published.','The event has been removed.'=>'The event has been removed.','The following couldn\'t be automatically embedded, so they were left out:'=>'The following couldn\'t be automatically embedded, so they were left out:','The full text cannot be empty. Fill it back in, or use "Discard" from the original email instead.'=>'The full text cannot be empty. Fill it back in, or use "Discard" from the original email instead.','The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus locks on it.'=>'The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus locks on it.','The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still.'=>'The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still.','The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting on your camera.'=>'The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting on your camera.','The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and fill the frame with the artwork.'=>'The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and fill the frame with the artwork.','The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and make sure you\'re close enough that the artwork fills the frame.'=>'The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and make sure you\'re close enough that the artwork fills the frame.','The Join application form and the Newsletter Subscribe form both require human verification before they accept a submission.'=>'The Join application form and the Newsletter Subscribe form both require human verification before they accept a submission.','The original published item could not be found.'=>'The original published item could not be found.','The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork clearly.'=>'The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork clearly.','The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural light source or adjust your camera\'s white balance.'=>'The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural light source or adjust your camera\'s white balance.','The photo has a strong color cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your phone\'s Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colors.'=>'The photo has a strong color cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your phone\'s Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colors.','The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works best.'=>'The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works best.','The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — diffuse light or shade gives more even tones.'=>'The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — diffuse light or shade gives more even tones.','The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.'=>'The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.','The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.'=>'The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.','The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch your phone\'s white balance to Daylight / Cloudy.'=>'The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch your phone\'s white balance to Daylight / Cloudy.','The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d day. Your submission stays as a draft until you decide.'=>'The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d day. Your submission stays as a draft until you decide.' . "\0" . 'The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d days. Your submission stays as a draft until you decide.','The removal link has expired. Please send another removal request.'=>'The removal link has expired. Please send another removal request.','The submission has been discarded.'=>'The submission has been discarded.','The title cannot be empty.'=>'The title cannot be empty.','The uploaded file could not be read.'=>'The uploaded file could not be read.','Their account and all published work have been permanently deleted.'=>'Their account and all published work have been permanently deleted.','There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or change your angle to eliminate it.'=>'There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or change your angle to eliminate it.','There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface.'=>'There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface.','There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface.'=>'There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface.','There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake.'=>'There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake.','There is no photo to restore.'=>'There is no photo to restore.','These confirmation links expire in 7 days.'=>'These confirmation links expire in 7 days.','These fields save without any preview — the first real look at how your colors, width, and logo combine is otherwise whatever email happens to go out next. Send yourself a sample using the settings currently saved above (save first if you just changed something and want the test to match).'=>'These fields save without any preview — the first real look at how your colors, width, and logo combine is otherwise whatever email happens to go out next. Send yourself a sample using the settings currently saved above (save first if you just changed something and want the test to match).','This address has bounced or been reported as spam — mail may no longer be reaching this artist.'=>'This address has bounced or been reported as spam — mail may no longer be reaching this artist.','This artist can\'t be reached through this form right now.'=>'This artist can\'t be reached through this form right now.','This artist has muted community broadcast messages.'=>'This artist has muted community broadcast messages.','This artist receives one daily digest of open applications instead of an email per application.'=>'This artist receives one daily digest of open applications instead of an email per application.','This community is currently full, so your application has joined the waitlist — when a member leaves, the next person in line is welcomed in.'=>'This community is currently full, so your application has joined the waitlist — when a member leaves, the next person in line is welcomed in.','This confirmation link expires in 7 days.'=>'This confirmation link expires in 7 days.','This confirmation link has already been used or is no longer valid. If you still want to leave, please request removal again from your account.'=>'This confirmation link has already been used or is no longer valid. If you still want to leave, please request removal again from your account.','This confirmation link is invalid or has already been used.'=>'This confirmation link is invalid or has already been used.','This confirms that your account and everything you published on %s have been permanently deleted, as you requested.'=>'This confirms that your account and everything you published on %s have been permanently deleted, as you requested.','This conflicts with Agnosis artist subdomains — both plugins would claim the same subdomain namespace.'=>'This conflicts with Agnosis artist subdomains — both plugins would claim the same subdomain namespace.','This email address belongs to an admitted artist.'=>'This email address belongs to an admitted artist.','This field cannot be edited here.'=>'This field cannot be edited here.','This is a one-off deliverability test from your Agnosis Settings → Email Inbox page. If you\'re reading this in your inbox (not spam), the community/transactional From identity is deliverable to this address.'=>'This is a one-off deliverability test from your Agnosis Settings → Email Inbox page. If you\'re reading this in your inbox (not spam), the community/transactional From identity is deliverable to this address.','This is a sample of the branded email shell — header, body text, a button, and (below) the footer card — built from whatever is currently saved on Settings → Branding.'=>'This is a sample of the branded email shell — header, body text, a button, and (below) the footer card — built from whatever is currently saved on Settings → Branding.','This is a TEST send — it previews the next issue using the current draft intro and recent activity. It was not counted as a real send and no subscribers were emailed. The unsubscribe link below is a non-functional placeholder.'=>'This is a TEST send — it previews the next issue using the current draft intro and recent activity. It was not counted as a real send and no subscribers were emailed. The unsubscribe link below